sentences: Under this item, the SBSTA closing plenary on 1 December took up activities implemented jointly under the pilot phase.
The SBSTA agreed to forward a draft decision to the COP.
The COP adopted the decision on 7 December.
Final Outcome: In its decision (FCCC/SBSTA/2012/L.27), the COP considered the reports on activities implemented jointly and decided to conclude the pilot phase for activities implemented jointly.
